dreisoft.tresos.tresosdb.api.model.v1.swcomponenttemplate.swcimplementation

Interface IPerInstanceMemorySize

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IEntity

    public interface IPerInstanceMemorySize
extends IEntity
    IPerInstanceMemorySize: Entity class of the tresosDB model.

    Resources needed by the allocation of PerInstanceMemory for each SWC instance. Note that these resources are not covered by an ObjectFileSection, because they are supposed to be allocated by the RTE.

    GENERATED CODE. DO NOT CHANGE!
